On MacOS 10.14.3 using Python 3.7.2_2 I am getting the following error when trying to install Cython.

`pip3 install Cython==0.26.1`

returns

```
SyntaxError: invalid syntax

```

comment_data.body:

2) Could you provide the actual syntax error that you are getting, i.e. the code line that it is complaining about?
